hjenglish.com/w/fingerprint\" target=\"_blank\">fingerprint</a> to gain access to the system<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tTaking one last look at the room, he was about to leave when a glass sculpture on a side table caught his eye. It was not that the style of the art piece did not fit in well with the overall d&eacute;cor of the office. Perhaps it was the delicate design , or it might have been the way the glass caught the light. Doug approached the sculpture and examined it closely. Prior, when he was doing the sweep of the room to debug, he already scanned the glass sculpture and the area around it.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169528019313/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827502/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827502\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p825925/\">双语美文：愿得一人心，白首不分离</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p839955/\">这3款外语学习类APP，老外最爱用！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p819214/\">新研究：世界最健康的5种饮食方式</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p839767/\">2017雅思考试时间表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767739/\">段子手的自白：我是如何从421进化到515的！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p843931/\">谷歌生日？9件关于Google你不知道的事情</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844765/\">好的吧，现在连狗都出来虐狗了[微笑.jpg]